  "description": {
    "de": "Mit dieser Klinge ist wirklich alles okey-dokey. Sogar doppelt!",
    "en": "These daggers are perfect for pushing Pineapis and shaking trees, or pushing Pineapis and grinding coffee, if that's what takes your fancy. Just remember: to the left, to the right, jump up and down and to the knees.",
    "es": "Estas dagas son ideales para cortar piñas o moler café. Hay quien las utiliza para trozear las manzanas y peras de la macedonia.",
    "fr": "Ces dagues sont parfaites pour pousser les ananas ou moudre le café. Certains s'en servent même pour taper des pommes et des poires.",
    "id": "47658",
    "pt": "Estas adagas são perfeitas para puxar bananas e moer café. Alguns até as usam para esmagar maças e peras."
  },
